service-part-edit-name-text =
    <b>Changing Spare Part Name 📝</b>

    Enter the new spare part name.
    For example: <i>"Engine oil 5W-30"</i>

    ✏️ <b>Enter the new name:</b>

service-part-edit-price-text =
    <b>Editing Total Cost 💰</b>

    Enter the new total cost of the spare part in rubles.

    Write using numbers, for example:
    ✅ 15000
    ✅ 123.45
    ✅ 543.21

    💵 <b>Enter the new amount:</b>

service-part-edit-quantity-text =
    <b>Changing Quantity 🔢</b>

    Enter the new quantity.
    Use only numbers.

    📦 <b>Enter the new quantity:</b>

service-part-edit-quantity-error-text =
    ❌ <b>Quantity Input Error</b>

    <b>Please enter a whole number greater than zero.</b>

    <b>Examples of correct input:</b>
    • 1
    • 5
    • 10

    📦 <b>Try again:</b>

service-part-edit-price-per-unit-text =
    <b>Changing Price Per Unit 💰</b>

    Enter the new price per unit in rubles.
    You can use numbers and a decimal point for kopecks.

    💵 <b>Enter the new price per item:</b>

service-part-edit-price-error-text =
    ❌ <b>Amount Input Error</b>

    <b>Please enter the amount using numbers.</b>
    You can use a period or comma for kopecks.

    <b>Examples of correct input:</b>
    ✅ 12500
    ✅ 5250.50
    ✅ 3,200

    💰 <b>Try again:</b>

